doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Password Reset - Recipe App
  body(style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; text-align: center;")
    table(style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);")
      tr
        td(style="padding: 20px;")
          h1(style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;") Password Reset
          p(style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;") You've requested to reset your password for Recipe App. To reset your password, please click the button below:
          a(href=resetLink, style="display: inline-block; background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 20px;") Reset My Password
          p(style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;") If the button above doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following URL into your web browser:
          p(style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin-top: 10px;") #{resetLink}
          p(style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;") This link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.
          p(style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;") If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email.
          p(style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;") If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at support@your-recipe-app.com.
        td(style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;")
          p(style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;") You're receiving this email because you requested a password reset for your Recipe App account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.
